Subject: drm/amd/display: Remove unused tunnel BW validation
Git-commit: 156374b2a6ce56ac744c75ce26649d421e48311d
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1
References: jsc#PED-13979 jsc#PED-14039 jsc#PED-14046 jsc#PED-14211 jsc#PED-14333 jsc#PED-14487 jsc#PED-14488 jsc#PED-14497 jsc#PED-14499 jsc#PED-15868

[Why & How]
The tunnel BW validation code has changed to the new one.
Remove the unused code.
The DP tunneling overhead is not updated in SST.
